1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:05,158
When you start the activities, they will follow the same order as this lesson.

2
00:00:05,108 --> 00:00:13,532
First, you do a warm-up: Staff will say examples: holiday photo, Documents, CV, shopping folder.

3
00:00:13,532 --> 00:00:16,005
You decide file or folder.

4
00:00:16,005 --> 00:00:20,584
Then you answer quick checks, so we know the key words make sense.

5
00:00:20,584 --> 00:00:28,614
Next, you practise the real computer skill: Open File Explorer and visit Desktop, Documents and Downloads.

6
00:00:28,614 --> 00:00:32,089
Keep returning to Documents as the main place.

7
00:00:32,089 --> 00:00:38,817
You may also type a short answer, for example: Type the folder we look in first for saved work.

8
00:00:38,817 --> 00:00:44,211
At the end, you finish with a stretch or reflection: Use a safe test file.

9
00:00:44,211 --> 00:00:48,016
Staff supports you to place it inside the new folder.

10
00:00:48,016 --> 00:00:50,567
Take one activity at a time.

11
00:00:50,567 --> 00:00:55,108
If you need help, ask staff, then try the next step yourself.

